    (17, "Combinaison de plongée planétaire (capitaine)", "Planet Diving Suit (Captain)", "Permet de modifier l'apparence d'EVE.", "Changes the appearance of EVE.", "Tenue de combat chargée en particules d'énergie explosives conçue pour être utilisée avec l'épée tachyonique. Lorsque vous enfilez cette tenue, vous devez aussi revêtir votre sens du devoir et votre courage héroïque.", "Combat suits charged with explosive particle energy. Designed to pair with the Tachyon Blade. Whenever you equip this suit, you must also equip your sense of duty to save others' lives.", "Où la trouver ?", "Where to find it ?", "Dans la boutique Tetrastar C&T", "Unknown", "/images/nano_suits/Planet_Diving_Suit_(Captain).webp", "/icons/star_fill_blue.webp", 1),
    (18, "Combinaison de plongée planétaire renforcée (7)", "", "Permet de modifier l'apparence d'EVE.", "Changes the appearance of EVE.", "La tenue de protection officielle du 7e escadron aéroporté. Le gilet de protection et la combinaison de plongée planétaire sont reliés l'un à l'autre afin de réduire les dégâts provoqués par le feu, la corrosion, les toxines et les shrapnels.", "", "Où la trouver ?", "Where to find it ?", "Dans la boutique Tetrastar C&T", "Unknown", "/images/nano_suits/unavailable.webp", "/icons/star_fill_blue.webp", 1),
    (19, "Combinaison de refroidissement", "Cooling Suit", "Permet de modifier l'apparence d'EVE.", "Changes the appearance of EVE.", "Cette tenue de refroidissement est conçue pour les individus en surchauffe constante. Si une personne normale l'enfilait, elle aurait trop froid pour bouger.", "This cooling suit is designed for individuals who are constantly overheating. This suit would leave a regular person too cold to move properly.", "Où la trouver ?", "Where to find it ?", "Dans la boutique Tetrastar C&T", "Unknown", "/images/nano_suits/Cooling_Suit.webp", "/icons/star_fill_blue.webp", 1),
    (20, "Combinaison des étoiles", "Stargazer Suit", "Permet de modifier l'apparence d'EVE.", "Changes the appearance of EVE.", "Ceux qui observent les étoiles sont les premiers à prendre conscience de leur destinée.", "The one who looks at the stars is the first to realise their destiny.", "Où la trouver ?", "Where to find it ?", "Dans la boutique Tetrastar C&T", "Unknown", "/images/nano_suits/Stargazer_Suit.webp", "/icons/star_fill_blue.webp", 1),
    (21, "", "Neurolink Suit", "Permet de modifier l'apparence d'EVE.", "Changes the appearance of EVE.", "", "Introducing the 'Ubiquitous' collection, a result of Tetrastar C&T's ambitious rebranding efforts. Infused with internal processors and nano elements, this ensemble boasts the ability to seamlessly connect and control nearby electronic devices, and was ultimately improved to become a pilot suit. However, amidst the departure of 'Galaxy' Alan from Tetrastar C&T, people dismissed the suit as nothing but a 'plugsuit' and protested for the reinstatement of Alan's creative vision.", "Où la trouver ?", "Where to find it ?", "Dans la boutique Tetrastar C&T", "Unknown", "/images/nano_suits/unavailable.webp", "/icons/star_fill_blue.webp", 1),
    (22, "Combinaison ouverte", "Keyhole Suit", "Permet de modifier l'apparence d'EVE.", "Changes the appearance of EVE.", "Cette tenue de la collection « Sens exotique » a été conçue par le styliste phare de Tetrastar C&T: « Galaxy » Alan. Bien que la poitrine soit peu couverte, la tenue est conçue pour vous envelopper d'un champ électromagnétique qui vous permet de recevoir l'énergie de l'univers.", "This is the 'Exotic Sense' collection outfit designed by Tetrastar C&T's lead designer, 'Galaxy' Alan. While the chest area is revealing, it is intended to cover you with an electromagnetic field so that you can receive the universe's energy.", "Où la trouver ?", "Where to find it ?", "Dans la boutique Tetrastar C&T", "Unknown", "/images/nano_suits/unavailable.webp", "/icons/star_fill_blue.webp", 1),
    (23, "Combinaison de plongée planétaire (6)", "Planet Diving Suit (6th)", "Permet de modifier l'apparence d'EVE.", "Changes the appearance of EVE.", "« Enfant né par une nuit étoilée. Avance et accomplis ta mission. Demeure inflexible face à l'adversité et façonne-nous un avenir radieux de tes mains. »", "'Children born on a starry night. Go forth and fulfil your mission. May you always fight back with an indomitable spirit, and may our future bloom in your hands.'", "Où la trouver ?", "Where to find it ?", "Dans la boutique Tetrastar C&T", "Unknown", "/images/nano_suits/Planet_Diving_Suit_(6th).webp", "/icons/star_fill_blue.webp", 1),
    (24, "Cyberlapin", "Cyber Bunny", "Permet de modifier l'apparence d'EVE.", "Changes the appearance of EVE.", "Cette tenue de la collection « Samedi jusqu'au bout de la nuit » a été conçue par le styliste phare de Tetrastar C&T: « Galaxy » Alan. Suite à de nombreux essais, nous avons réussi à installer des oreilles mobiles reliées au système cybernétique. On ne vous surnommera plus «cyberlapin » par hasard.", "This is the 'Sleepless Saturday Night' collection outfit designed by Tetrastar C&T's lead designer, 'Galaxy' Alan. After countless trials and errors, the rabbit ears were successfully made to be moveable through a cybernetic link. Now, you can truly be called a Cyber Bunny.", "Où la trouver ?", "Where to find it ?", "Dans la boutique Tetrastar C&T", "Unknown", "/images/nano_suits/Cyber_Bunny.webp", "/icons/star_fill_blue.webp", 1),
    (25, "Cybermage", "Cyber Magician", "Permet de modifier l'apparence d'EVE.", "Changes the appearance of EVE.", "L'alliance élégante du justaucorps et de la veste à queue-de-pie. Les micro-pilotes furtifs intégrés au niveau des poignets vous permettent d'escroqu- euh, je veux dire d'utiliser le système de furtivité intégré !", "Combine the fancy style of a leotard with a tailcoat. Featuring micro-stealth drivers in each wrist, you can easily steal—l mean, you can easily utilise your skills with the embedded stealth-drive technology!", "Où la trouver ?", "Where to find it ?", "Dans la boutique Tetrastar C&T", "Unknown", "/images/nano_suits/Cyber_Magician.webp", "/icons/star_fill_blue.webp", 1),
    (26, "Euphorie du pilote", "Racer's High", "Permet de modifier l'apparence d'EVE.", "Changes the appearance of EVE.", "Cette tenue de la collection « Sens exotique » a été conçue par le styliste phare de Tetrastar C&T : « Galaxy » Alan. On raconte que les nano-éléments intégrés possèdent un code malveillant semblable à une drogue électronique capable d'augmenter la vitesse.", "This is the 'Exotic Sense' collection outfit designed by Tetrastar C&T's lead designer, 'Galaxy' Alan. It is said that the embedded Nano Elements are loaded with a malicious code that is like some kind of electronic drug so that you can boast enhanced speed.", "Où la trouver ?", "Where to find it ?", "Dans la boutique Tetrastar C&T", "Unknown", "/images/nano_suits/Racer-s_High.webp", "/icons/star_fill_blue.webp", 1),
    (27, "Fille de l'air", "Air Ace", "Permet de modifier l'apparence d'EVE.", "Changes the appearance of EVE.", "Désireuse d'exploiter les dernières avancées scientifiques et la réalité augmentée, Tetrastar C&T a intégré des nano-éléments à sa collection. Hélas, certaines innovations ne trouvent pas leur public. Bien qu'elle ait fait appel aux plus grands noms pour créer ce blouson aviateur, les amateurs de mode du monde entier se demandèrent si la filiale n'avait pas totalement perdu la tête.", "Tetrastar C&T infused Nano Elements into their collection, aiming to champion data science and augmented reality technology through their designs. However, not every innovation resonated with the public. While the company touted the expertise of top guns manifest in their Ace series aviator's bomber jacket, the most sophisticated response they received was: Are they completely out of their minds?'", "Où la trouver ?", "Where to find it ?", "Dans la boutique Tetrastar C&T", "Unknown", "/images/nano_suits/Air_Ace.webp", "/icons/star_fill_blue.webp", 1),
    (28, "Force quotidienne", "Daily Force", "Permet de modifier l'apparence d'EVE.", "Changes the appearance of EVE.", "Tetrastar C&T est là pour vous. Une tenue pleine de force issue de la collection « Quotidien ». Pour un look confortable, confiant et amical.", "Tetrastar C&T is here for you. A casual force outfit from the Daily Collection that makes you feel more friendly, comfortable, and confident.", "Où la trouver ?", "Where to find it ?", "Dans la boutique Tetrastar C&T", "Unknown", "/images/nano_suits/Daily_Force.webp", "/icons/star_fill_blue.webp", 1),
    (29, "Frissons de la vitesse", "Speeder's High", "Permet de modifier l'apparence d'EVE.", "Changes the appearance of EVE.", "Cette tenue de la collection « Sens exotique » a été conçue par le styliste phare de Tetrastar C&T : « Galaxy » Alan. Elle serait équipée du « système vitesse stellaire », qui injecte de la dopamine à son propriétaire et lui permet de profiter pleinement de l'instant présent.", "This is the 'Exotic Sense' collection outfit designed by Tetrastar C&T's lead designer, 'Galaxy' Alan. It is said that the outfit features the 'Speed Star System', which injects electric dopamine signals to the wearer's body so that the wearer can fully enjoy the race.", "Où la trouver ?", "Where to find it ?", "Dans la boutique Tetrastar C&T", "Unknown", "/images/nano_suits/Speeder-s_High.webp", "/icons/star_fill_blue.webp", 1),
    (30, "Haut court punk", "Punk Top", "Permet de modifier l'apparence d'EVE.", "Changes the appearance of EVE.", "Ce n'est pas grave si cette tenue est déchirée. Ce n'est pas grave si elle est vraiment bien déchirée, parce que c'est tendance. Avec un haut court trop cool.", "It's okay if it's a little torn. It's okay even if it's torn a lot more than you think because this is the style. With a cool tank top.", "Où la trouver ?", "Where to find it ?", "Dans la boutique Tetrastar C&T", "Unknown", "/images/nano_suits/Punk_Top.webp", "/icons/star_fill_blue.webp", 1),
    (31, "Hydrangea", "Hydrangea", "Permet de modifier l'apparence d'EVE.", "Changes the appearance of EVE.", "Cette tenue de la collection « Deuxième lune orientale » a été conçue par le styliste phare de Tetrastar C&T: « Galaxy » Alan. Ultime création de l'égérie du prêt-à-porter avant son départ de la firme, ce modèle est rapidement entré en tête des ventes. Suite à son évincement, Alan a évoqué le lancement de sa propre marque, avant de disparaître mystérieusement, ne laissant derrière lui que questions et suppositions quant à son sort.", "This is the 'Second Oriental Moon' collection design from Tetrastar C&T's lead designer, 'Galaxy' Alan. This attire swiftly became a top seller as the final creation by Alan before his departure from Tetrastar C&T. Following his exit, Alan hinted at the launch of his own brand in the near future. Yet, Alan mysteriously vanished, leaving behind questions and speculations about his fate.", "Où la trouver ?", "Where to find it ?", "Dans la boutique Tetrastar C&T", "Unknown", "/images/nano_suits/Hydrangea.webp", "/icons/star_fill_blue.webp", 1),
    (32, "", "Cyber Illusionist", "Permet de modifier l'apparence d'EVE.", "Changes the appearance of EVE.", "", "A leotard, a tailcoat, and seven tool kits. You are an unmatched illusionist with nimble fingers.", "Où la trouver ?", "Where to find it ?", "Dans la boutique Tetrastar C&T", "Unknown", "/images/nano_suits/unavailable.webp", "/icons/star_fill_blue.webp", 1),
    (33, "Ingénieure d'Orca", "Orca Engineer", "Permet de modifier l'apparence d'EVE.", "Changes the appearance of EVE.", "Une combinaison d'ingénieur renforcée, résistante au feu, au froid et aux chocs. Cette tenue équipée de poches à outils extrêmement pratiques a été spécifiquement conçue pour un usage industriel. Toute utilisation lors de combats contre les Naytibas entraînera l'annulation de la garantie.", "A reinforced engineering suit that provides strong flame/cold protection and cushioning while also having a convenient tool pouch. Please be warned that it was designed only for industrial use. Combat with Naytibas will void the warranty.", "Où la trouver ?", "Where to find it ?", "Dans la boutique Tetrastar C&T", "Unknown", "/images/nano_suits/Orca_Engineer.webp", "/icons/star_fill_blue.webp", 1),
    (34, "Ingénieure recycleuse", "Junk Engineer", "Permet de modifier l'apparence d'EVE.", "Changes the appearance of EVE.", "Conformément à sa politique de droit aux réparations, Tetrastar a intégré à ses produits des nano-éléments qui donnent accès aux manuels de maintenance. Inspirée par cette approche révolutionnaire, C&T a lancé sa toute dernière gamme de tenues d'ingénieurs avec accès instantané aux manuels de réparation de tous leurs produits grâce à l'intégration de nano-éléments.", "Tetrastar's integration of Nano Elements into its merchandise allows access to repair manuals as part of their commitment to the 'Right-to-Repair' campaign. Inspired by this innovative approach, C&T introduced their latest engineer outfits, providing wearers with instant access to repair manuals for all their products through Nano Element integration.", "Où la trouver ?", "Where to find it ?", "Dans la boutique Tetrastar C&T", "Unknown", "/images/nano_suits/Junk_Engineer.webp", "/icons/star_fill_blue.webp", 1),
    (35, "Jean déchiré FourSeconds", "FourSeconds Destroyed Denim", "Permet de modifier l'apparence d'EVE.", "Changes the appearance of EVE.", "Cette tenue complète en jean déchiré a été créée par FourSeconds, une filiale de Tetrastar C&T. Conçue pour captiver les clients en un temps fugace, le nom de la marque fait écho à la théorie psychologique bien connue selon laquelle les premières impressions sont fixées en seulement quatre secondes.", "This destroyed denim outfit originates from FourSeconds, Tetrastar C&T'S SPA sub-brand. Designed to captivate customers within the fleeting span of time, the brand's nomenclature echoes the renowned psychological theory, which asserts that first impressions are determined in a mere four seconds.", "Où la trouver ?", "Where to find it ?", "Dans la boutique Tetrastar C&T", "Unknown", "/images/nano_suits/unavailable.webp", "/icons/star_fill_blue.webp", 1),
    (36, "Jean FourSeconds", "FourSeconds Denim", "Permet de modifier l'apparence d'EVE.", "Changes the appearance of EVE.", "Cette tenue complète en jean a été créée par FourSeconds, une filiale de Tetrastar C&T. Conçue pour captiver les clients en un temps fugace, le nom de la marque fait écho à la théorie psychologique bien connue selon laquelle les premières impressions sont fixées en seulement quatre secondes.", "This denim outfit originates from FourSeconds, Tetrastar C&T's SPA sub-brand. Designed to captivate customers within the fleeting span of time, the brand's nomenclature echoes the renowned psychological theory, which asserts that first impressions are determined in a mere four seconds.", "Où la trouver ?", "Where to find it ?", "Dans la boutique Tetrastar C&T", "Unknown", "/images/nano_suits/unavailable.webp", "/icons/star_fill_blue.webp", 1),
