    (62, "Pionnière d'Orca", "Orca Pathfinder", "Permet de modifier l'apparence d'EVE.", "Changes the appearance of EVE.", "Cette combinaison environnementale est le fruit de la collaboration entre Tetrastar C&T et Orca Aerospace. Néanmoins, beaucoup n'y virent qu'un maillot de bain hors de prix, ignorant que cette seconde peau devait être portée en dessous d'une combinaison spatiale. La majorité des gens pensèrent que c'était une énième pirouette marketing de la part de Tetrastar C&T.", "This specialised environment outfit was the result of a collaborative effort between Tetrastar C&T and Orca Aerospace Company. However, many perceived it simply as an exorbitantly priced swimsuit, unaware that its purpose was to be worn underneath a space suit. The concept was dismissed by some as just another weird marketing ploy by Tetrastar C&T.", "Où la trouver ?", "Where to find it ?", "Dans la boutique Tetrastar C&T", "Unknown", "/images/nano_suits/unavailable.webp", "/icons/star_fill_blue.webp", 1),
